Title: Tenuto
Description: ['Music video directed by Kousuke Sugimoto for the song ', Tenuto, ' by Handsome Kenya on the mini album "Black Frame." The album had two releases, one which included a bonus DVD featuring this music video and a short documentary about Handsome Kenya. The music video was posted on YouTube along with a preview of the documentary in a single video. This entry only accounts for the runtime of the music video.']
